The U6 promoter-2 kb BsmBI-BsmBI filler cassette of lentiCRISPRv2 hygro (Addgene plasmid #98291) was removed by KpnI/NheI digestion and a KpnI-XhoI-BsrGI-NheI double-stranded oligonucleotide sequence was cloned in its place between the KpnI and NheI restriction sites (see also lentiCas9 puro, Addgene plasmid #104994; lentiCas9 neo, Addgene plasmid #104996; and lentiCas9 blast, Addgene plasmid #104997).
